window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Most will die. Some will survive. A small few will thrive.</p> <p></p> <p>My party and I cleared the dungeon in Griffith Park, got a ton of loot, and saved the safe zone. So far so good, but Los Angeles is a big city with a bunch of safe zones that need saving, and there are ton of innocent people who are gonna die if we can’t do it. Luckily, my party has the skills to get it done.</p> <p></p> <p>Unfortunately, The System isn’t so simple. There is a power monster lurking beneath the Earth in SoCal, and it is planning to trigger a massive Earthquake that will destroy the entire west coast, safe zone or not. If we kill it, we’re heroes forever. If we fail, everybody dies. No biggie.</p>"; 
